[{"id":"623ebeff2ce876714595048837db774a","from":"J. Epstein","from_email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to":"Craig@SchemeDesigners.com","to_list":[{"name":"Craig@SchemeDesigners.com","email":"Craig@SchemeDesigners.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Re: Gulfstream IIB Paint Scheme Design","date":"2006-11-28T15:55:37.000Z","formatted_date":"Nov 28, 2006","formatted_time":"3:55 PM","body":"2a1 is nice\n\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: \"Craig Barnett, Scheme Designers, Inc.\" <Craig@schemedesigners.com>\nTo: jetcare@aol.com; jeeproject@yahoo.com\nSent: Tuesday, November 28, 2006 10:50:33 AM\nSubject: Gulfstream IIB Paint Scheme Design\n\n\nHi:\n \nThank you for your comments on the \u201ccarpet\u201d scheme.  The scheme used the scaled stripe pattern from the carpets.  I agree that there were a lot of stripes.\n \nI have prepared some modifications of the schemes to reduce the number of stripes.  Please take a look at http://www.schemedesigners.com/GulfstreamIIB and let me have further comments.\n \nAlso, don\u2019t hesitate to let me know any additional design directions you would like me to pursue.\n \nBest regards,\n \nCraig Barnett\nScheme Designers, Inc.\n210 Brookside Avenue\nCresskill, NJ   07626\nUSA\n201-569-7785\n917-405-3862 - Cell\ncraig@schemedesigners.com\nwww.schemedesigners.com\n\n","body_html":"<html><head><style type=\"text/css\"><!-- DIV {margin:0px;} --></style></head><body><div style=\"font-family:times new roman, new york, times, serif;font-size:12pt\"><DIV style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif\">2a1 is nice<BR><BR>\n<DIV style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif\">----- Original Message ----<BR>From: \"Craig Barnett, Scheme Designers, Inc.\" &lt;Craig@schemedesigners.com&gt;<BR>To: jetcare@aol.com; jeeproject@yahoo.com<BR>Sent: Tuesday, November 28, 2006 10:50:33 AM<BR>Subject: Gulfstream IIB Paint Scheme Design<BR><BR>\n<STYLE>\n<!--\n _filtered {font-family:\"Arial Black\";\npanose-1:2 11 10 4 2 1 2 2 2 4;}\n/* Style Definitions */\n p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{margin:0in;\nmargin-bottom:.0001pt;\nfont-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\";}\na:link, span.MsoHyperlink\n\t{color:blue;\ntext-decoration:underline;}\na:visited, span.MsoHyperlinkFollowed\n\t{color:purple;\ntext-decoration:underline;}\nspan.EmailStyle17\n\t{\nfont-family:Arial;\ncolor:windowtext;}\n _filtered {\nmargin:1.0in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\ndiv.Section1\n\t{}\n-->\n</STYLE>\n\n<DIV class=Section1>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Hi:</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Thank you for your comments on the \u201ccarpet\u201d scheme.&nbsp; The scheme used the scaled stripe pattern from the carpets.&nbsp; I agree that there were a lot of stripes.</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">I have prepared some modifications of the schemes to reduce the number of stripes.&nbsp; Please take a look at <A href=\"http://www.schemedesigners.com/GulfstreamIIB\" target=_blank rel=nofollow>http://www.schemedesigners.com/GulfstreamIIB</A> and let me have further comments.</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Also, don\u2019t hesitate to let me know any additional design directions you would like me to pursue.</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Best regards,</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Craig Barnett</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Arial Black\" size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial Black'\">Scheme Designers, Inc.</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">210 Brookside Avenue</SPAN></FONT></I></EM></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Cresskill</SPAN></FONT></I></EM><EM><I><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">, NJ &nbsp; 07626</SPAN></FONT></I></EM></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">USA</SPAN></FONT></I></EM></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">201-569-7785</SPAN></FONT></I></EM></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">917-405-3862 - Cell</SPAN></FONT></I></EM></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><A href=\"mailto:craig@schemedesigners.com\" target=_blank rel=nofollow><EM><I><FONT face=Arial color=black><SPAN style=\"COLOR: windowtext; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; TEXT-DECORATION: none\">craig@schemedesigners.com</SPAN></FONT></I></EM></A></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><A href=\"http://www.schemedesigners.com/\" target=_blank rel=nofollow><EM><I><FONT face=Arial color=black><SPAN style=\"COLOR: windowtext; FONT-FAMILY: Ari